# Manuscript markdown is a build artifact derived from
# content/{text}/manuscript.{lang}.json — see Plans/manuscript-format-plan.md
# Decision 2. The .build/ path is the default during development; the
# content/ovid-metamorphoses/book*.md path is where `make manuscript-md`
# writes during a build so downstream stages keep working.
site/generator/.build/
content/ovid-metamorphoses/book*.md
content/marvell-hortus/book*.md

# iOS app
app/build/
app/ReadingRoom.xcodeproj/
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
DerivedData/
